Description_lang: Angus Ironfist was born into this world with a desire to fight. He loves going toe-to-toe with any rival, and can best them with a combination of martial combat, grapples, wrestling, and well-timed punches and kicks.
AuraDescription_lang: Angus Ironfist never backs down from a fight, and never gives up!

description_blz.en_US: Angus Ironfist was born into this world with a desire to fight. He loves going toe-to-toe with any rival, and can best them with a combination of martial combat, grapples, wrestling, and well-timed punches and kicks.
description_blz.es_MX: Angus Puño de Hierro vino a este mundo con el deseo de pelear. Le encanta enfrentarse con cualquier rival y puede derrotarlo con una combinación de combate marcial, agarres, lucha y puños y patadas oportunos.
description_blz.pt_BR: Angus Punho de Ferro nasceu com uma vontade que nunca se satisfaz de lutar. Ele adora sair no mano a mano com qualquer rival, e consegue superá-los com uma combinação de combate marcial, agarrões e luta-livre, além de socos e chutes muito bem encaixados.
description_blz.de_DE: Angus Eisenfaust war von jüngster Kindheit an von Kampfeswillen durchdrungen. Er liebt es, sich mit dem Gegner von Angesicht zu Angesicht wiederzufinden, und bezwingt ihn mit einer Kombination aus Kampfkunst, Grifftechniken, Ringen und gut abgepassten Schlägen und Tritten.
description_blz.en_GB: Angus Ironfist was born into this world with a desire to fight. He loves going toe-to-toe with any rival, and can best them with a combination of martial combat, grapples, wrestling, and well-timed punches and kicks.
description_blz.es_ES: Angus Puño de Hierro vino a este mundo con ganas de luchar. Le encanta enfrentarse a cualquier rival, al que puede ganar con una combinación de combate marcial, presas, lucha libre y patadas y puñetazos oportunos.
description_blz.fr_FR: Angus Poing-de-Fer est né avec le désir de se battre. Il aime faire mordre la poussière à tous ceux qui lui cherchent des noises en combinant prises, techniques de lutte et coups de poing ou de pied.
description_blz.it_IT: Angus Pugnoferreo è nato col desiderio di combattere. Ama gli scontri faccia a faccia contro qualsiasi avversario ed è capace di sopraffare chiunque combinando le arti marziali, le prese, la lotta libera e un assortimento vario di pugni e calci.
description_blz.ru_RU: Ангус Железный Кулак чуть ли не с рождения уже знал, что его призвание – сражаться. Он готов сойтись в бою с любым соперником и обрушить на него весь свой арсенал – приемы боевых искусств и стилей борьбы, захваты и точные удары руками и ногами.
description_blz.ko_KR: 앵거스 아이언피스트의 삶의 원동력은 오로지 전투에 대한 열망뿐입니다. 그는 정면 대결을 선호하며 능숙한 잡기와 정확한 타격 등을 고루 섞어 적을 제압합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 安格斯‧鐵拳生來就渴望戰鬥。他熱愛和任何對手面對面較量，並靠著一連串的武術、扭打、摔角和時機絕佳的拳擊腳踢來打贏對手。
description_blz.zh_CN: 安古斯·铁拳是天生的战士，热衷于和任何对手单挑。他将武术、擒拿、摔跤等技术结合在了一起，出拳踢脚的时机精准老辣，在战斗中无往不利。
